import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['delay'], bins=20, edgecolor='black')
    plt.xlabel('Delay')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.boxplot(data['distance'])
    plt.ylabel('Distance')
    plt.xticks([1], ['Flights'])
    plt.title('What is the average distance of flights?')
    plt.axhline(data['distance'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f"Average: {data['distance'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    origin_counts = data['origin'].value_counts()
    destination_counts = data['destination'].value_counts()
    
    combined_counts = pd.concat([origin_counts, destination_counts], axis=1)
    combined_counts.columns = ['Origin', 'Destination']
    
    ax = combined_counts.plot(kind='bar', rot=45)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.title("What is the most common origin and destination for flights?")
    plt.tight_layout()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%m%d%y', errors='ignore')
    date_counts = data['date'].value_counts().sort_index()
    
    plt.plot(date_counts.index, date_counts.values)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title("What is the distribution of flight dates?", wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
